casebody.data:
Sookram SUNDERDAT, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Samuel M. MANIGAULT and Board of Trustees, Newark Housing Authority, Defendants-Respondents,
and
Nazir Muhammed and Fahiym Muhammed, Defendants. C-980 September Term 2018
082225 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 13, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000924-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
